overview: Momok III is a horror film that combines several ghost stories in one film that is Dendam Maisarah, Penunggu Pusaka and Roh Jelmaan. This story is a mere fabrication and has nothing to do with those who are still alive or who have died. If there are any similarities, it is not intentional and happened by chance. Hope you are all entertained.
title: Momok III
